<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News]]></title><link/> https://sputniknews.com/新闻<atom:link href="https://rsshub.app/sputniknews" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)]]></description><generator> RSSHub</generator><webmaster> i@diygod.me (DIY神)</webmaster><language> zh-cn</language><lastbuilddate> 2023 年 5 月 26 日星期五 15:17:08 GMT</lastbuilddate><ttl> 120 </ttl><item><title><![CDATA[Jeff Monson: US Elite Mutes Russian Media to Keep Ukraine Conflict Raging On]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110609400" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1a/1110608418_0:0:2200:1546_1440x900_80_0_1_b58678480d3b368d018f606c048a2a2b.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110608400" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/jeff-monson-us-elite-mutes-russian-media-to-keep-ukraine-conflict-raging-on-1110609400.html?share-img=1110608400"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / RIA Novosti</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">Jeff Monson 在卢甘斯克人民共和国 (LPR)</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="Jeff Monson in Lugansk People's Republic (LPR) - Sputnik International, 1920, 26.05.2023" title="卢甘斯克人民共和国 (LPR) 的杰夫·蒙森 (Jeff Monson)" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1a/1110608418_0:0:2200:1239_1920x0_80_0_0_d2946bf4288b500a3685c607b520a237.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1a/1110608418_0:0:2200:1239_640x0_80_0_0_8a8749081b792e0fbc4a12cf75e79f78.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1a/1110608418_0:0:2200:1239_1280x0_80_0_0_afeecc5b98d23ce29f2d84162d84b482.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1a/1110608418_0:0:2200:1239_1920x0_80_0_0_d2946bf4288b500a3685c607b520a237.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / 俄新社</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">叶卡捷琳娜布林诺娃</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_ekaterina_blinova/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:e.blinova@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="exclusive">独家的</div><div class="article__announce-text">因反对华盛顿的乌克兰政策而放弃美国公民身份的传奇综合格斗 (MMA) 选手杰夫·蒙森告诉人造卫星，美国精英正在利用乌克兰冲突获利，并压制其他说法以维持对峙。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 52 岁的传奇“雪人”杰弗里·威廉·蒙森 (Jeffrey William Monson) 在 89 场战斗中取得了惊人的 61 场胜利，他告诉人造卫星：“您不必成为政治学家就可以了解<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/my-country-does-terrible-things-mma-fighter-jeff-monson-on-why-he-renounced-us-citizenship-1110590609.html" target="_blank">真正发生的事情</a>，因为我们看到了这种情况的发生。” .</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">杰夫认为，华盛顿企图尽可能延长乌克兰冲突的时间只会让美国精英受益。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “这场 [冲突] 有利于美国的大公司，有利于美国的领导人，有利于从这些公司获得资金用于竞选连任的政府领导人，有利于他们的政党，”蒙森告诉人造卫星网。 “非常非常少的人从中受益，国会议员，大企业。这就是美国卷入这场冲突的原因，不是因为普通美国人想要这场[代理人]战争。不，因为媒体已经把它卖给了普通美国人他们认为他们在支持一些好的东西。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110609400" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/jeff-monson-us-elite-mutes-russian-media-to-keep-ukraine-conflict-raging-on-1110609400.html?share-block=1110609770" data-title="&amp;quot;This [conflict] benefits the big corporations of America, which benefits the leaders of America, the government leaders who get money from these corporations for the reelection campaigns, for their political parties,&amp;quot; Monson told Sputnik. &amp;quot;So very, very few people benefit from this, the Congress people, the big businesses. And that&amp;#x27;s why America is in this conflict, not because ordinary Americans want this [proxy] war. No, because the media has sold this to ordinary Americans that they think they&amp;#x27;re supporting something good.&amp;quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="social"><div class="ria-tweet"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-conversation="none"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> 📹 MMA 拳击手 Jeff Monson 关于美国发动战争的原因<br><br>Sputnik 专访的摘录<a href="https://t.co/lCAKOkr8gV">pic.twitter.com/lCAKOkr8gV</a></p> -人造卫星 (@SputnikInt) <a href="https://twitter.com/SputnikInt/status/1662020315206107142?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 5 月 26 日</a></blockquote></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这位 MMA 传奇人物于 2018 年 5 月获得俄罗斯公民身份，并成为莫斯科附近克拉斯诺戈尔斯克市的一名议员。早些时候，他被证明是顿巴斯的热心支持者，顿巴斯在 2014 年 2 月乌克兰总统维克托·亚努科维奇被非法罢免后抵制基辅政权。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “我去过顿涅茨克和卢甘斯克，可能已经去过 11 或 12 次了，”他说。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110609400" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/jeff-monson-us-elite-mutes-russian-media-to-keep-ukraine-conflict-raging-on-1110609400.html?share-block=1110609405" data-title="&amp;quot;I&amp;#x27;ve been to Donetsk and Lugansk, maybe 11 or 12 times already,&amp;quot; he said."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="social"><div class="ria-tweet"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> 📹 在接受 Sputnik MMA 拳击手 Jeff Monson 的独家采访时解释了为什么他不支持美国政府实施的政策<a href="https://t.co/KG2UUVPTS3">pic.twitter.com/KG2UUVPTS3</a></p> -人造卫星 (@SputnikInt) <a href="https://twitter.com/SputnikInt/status/1662019507378958336?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 5 月 26 日</a></blockquote></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">今年4月下旬，杰夫宣布放弃美国国籍，原因是他反对美国政府现行政策，包括对乌克兰的军事化。他在 5 月言出必行，将美国护照交给了土耳其伊斯坦布尔的美国领事馆。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">乌克兰“待售” </h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “正如 [乌克兰总统沃洛德米尔] 泽伦斯基刚刚宣布的那样，他在电视上宣布与贝莱德、[JP] 摩根大通、高盛以及他与之交易的这些美国公司进行合作，乌克兰也与之进行交易。乌克兰如何进行交易和他们一起？乌克兰没钱。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110609400" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/jeff-monson-us-elite-mutes-russian-media-to-keep-ukraine-conflict-raging-on-1110609400.html?share-block=1110609409" data-title="&quot;As [Ukrainian President Volodymyr] Zelensky just announced, he was on TV announcing his cooperation with BlackRock, with [JP] Morgan Chase, Goldman Sachs, these American corporations that he made deals with, Ukraine made deals with. How does Ukraine make deals with them? Ukraine has no money.&quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">问题是泽连斯基将乌克兰挂牌出售——据蒙森说，这就是他要支付账单的方式。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “他卖掉了公用事业，他卖掉了交通工具，”这位 MMA 传奇继续说道。 “他在推销刑罚制度。他在推销交通；他在推销供水。他在向美国公司推销实体设施和公用事业。因此，在冲突之后，这些美国公司 [will] 进来，帮助‘重建’乌克兰。但他们将拥有乌克兰。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这些发展不符合普通乌克兰人的利益，但他们的意见不会被考虑，因为泽连斯基也在“出卖他们”，杰夫指出：“[乌克兰]人民现在将成为名副其实的工资奴隶，不是美国的奴隶，而是美国公司的奴隶。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">美国精英不希望乌克兰冲突结束</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">蒙森表示，一般来说，美国当权派正在煽动冲突，以耗尽乌克兰、让俄罗斯流血并破坏欧洲，从而使其更加依赖美国。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “美国摧毁了北溪管道，现在美国是新的供应商，而不是俄罗斯，但美国是欧洲的新天然气供应商，欧洲急需它。但他们以四倍于俄罗斯的价格出售它他们为了。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110609400" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/jeff-monson-us-elite-mutes-russian-media-to-keep-ukraine-conflict-raging-on-1110609400.html?share-block=1110609772" data-title="&quot;America destroyed the Nord Stream pipeline, now America is the new supplier, not Russia, but America is the new supplier of gas to Europe, which needs it badly. But they're selling it at four times the price that Russia sold it to them for.&quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">蒙森表示，由于旷日持久的冲突正是美国精英及其同伙想要的，因此他们破坏了同时进行的俄乌和平谈判以及时任以色列总理纳夫塔利<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230206/naftali-bennetts-inconvenient-recollection-1107024858.html" target="_blank">贝内特在 2022 年 3 月的解决努力</a>也就不足为奇了。在 2023 年 2 月的重磅采访中，贝内特回忆说，事实证明，俄罗斯和乌克兰是务实的谈判代表；法国和德国准备达成妥协。但英国和美国推动了持续的敌对行动。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “现在中国也试图通过谈判达成和平协议，”杰夫继续说道。 “美国说：‘走开，走开。不要听他们的，我们不想结束这场冲突’。美国真的不想结束这场冲突。它允许人们死去，因为他们想要这些公司赚钱。这就是他们在美国的看法：公司先于人。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">美国政府审查替代叙述</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美国精英如何设法向美国公众推销其在乌克兰的代理人战争？根据 Monson 的说法，他们通过消除不便的真相和扼杀替代性叙述来实现这一目标。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “原因是，美国，尤其是美国政治家，要说的关于美国的第一件事是什么？‘我们有民主，我们有自由。世界没有自由。我们有。自由，自由，自由。&#39;好吧，那是怎样的自由？如果生活在美国的人们受到审查，他们只被展示一个职位，他们被告知要怎么想。美国人真的不知道，大多数美国人不知道发生了什么在世界上。这正是他们在大众媒体上听到的。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110609400" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/jeff-monson-us-elite-mutes-russian-media-to-keep-ukraine-conflict-raging-on-1110609400.html?share-block=1110609774" data-title="&amp;quot;The reason is that, what&amp;#x27;s the number one thing America, or especially an American politician, is going to say about America? &amp;#x27;We have democracy, we have freedom. The world doesn&amp;#x27;t have freedom. We have. Freedom, Freedom, Freedom.&amp;#x27; Well, how is that freedom? If the people who live in America are censored and they&amp;#x27;re only shown one position and they&amp;#x27;re told what to think. Americans literally have no idea, the bulk of Americans have no idea of what&amp;#x27;s going on in the world. It&amp;#x27;s just what they hear on mass media.&amp;quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这位 MMA 传奇人物说，就其本身而言，美国媒体公司不仅在“误导”人们，而且公然向他们撒谎。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="social"><div class="ria-tweet"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-conversation="none"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> 📹 在接受 Sputnik 的独家采访时，MMA 拳击手杰夫·蒙森 (Jeff Monson) 直言不讳地指出普通美国公民对他们国家以外发生的事情一无所知<a href="https://t.co/E1YCFmCH4o">pic.twitter.com/E1YCFmCH4o</a></p> -人造卫星 (@SputnikInt) <a href="https://twitter.com/SputnikInt/status/1662021149486612482?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 5 月 26 日</a></blockquote></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “这样你就可以控制人民。你不必用枪强迫人们。在美国，他们不会拿枪指着你的头说，‘嘿，你需要这样做。’不，不，不。他们教育你，告诉你发生了什么，他们想让你相信什么。然后你就会自由地做他们想做的事。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">结果，美国人开始接受当权派的说法，并“自由地”支持美国在乌克兰发动的代理人战争。他们认为俄罗斯是一个“坏人”，他们认为它“入侵”了乌克兰，他们对基辅<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/beatings-stabbings--electric-shocks-donetsk-militia-vets-ordeal-in-ukraines-torture-chambers-1110480282.html" target="_blank">对顿巴斯平民长达九年的战争</a>一无所知，蒙森说。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “你从来没有听说过它，因为美国媒体没有告诉你，”他对美国观众说。 “因此，当媒体可以控制局势时，政府就可以在没有人民反抗的情况下为所欲为。这就是他们封锁人造卫星的原因。这就是他们封锁 RT 的原因，这就是他们封锁俄罗斯不同媒体的原因，因为他们不希望人们有其他选择， <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230509/mariupol-residents-reveal-how-kiev-nazis-turned-sacred-may-9-victory-day-into-massacre-in-2014-1110164374.html" target="_blank">看到不同的观点</a>。看，如果这是你知道的唯一方式，那么你当然会相信，因为这就是你被告知的全部。这就是你的全部相信。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110609400" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/jeff-monson-us-elite-mutes-russian-media-to-keep-ukraine-conflict-raging-on-1110609400.html?share-block=1110610188" data-title="&amp;quot;You never heard of it because the American media doesn&amp;#x27;t tell you,&amp;quot; he noted, addressing the American audience. &amp;quot;And so when the media can control the situation, the government is able to do what they want without the people rebelling. And so that&amp;#x27;s why they blocked Sputnik. That&amp;#x27;s why they blocked RT, that&amp;#x27;s why they blocked the different outlets in Russia, because they don&amp;#x27;t want people to have an alternative, to see a different perspective. Look, if this is the only way that you know, then of course you&amp;#x27;re going to believe that because that&amp;#x27;s all you&amp;#x27;re told. That&amp;#x27;s all you believe.&amp;quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2"> “这是我们的土地”</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">杰夫多次访问过顿巴斯，他知道他在说什么。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “我一直在前线，我看到了士兵们的所作所为，”他说。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">上一次，大概是五六个星期前，他去了顿巴斯，与过去九年来一直为土地而战的士兵交谈。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “我和一个男人，一个士兵交谈，我说，‘你为什么在这里？’他捡起地面亲吻它说，‘这是俄罗斯。这是我们的，伙计。我们必须保护它。我的亲戚住在这里，我的祖父母，他们的祖父母。这就是我们。这是我的爱。我会为这个地方献出生命。我会为我的国家、我的战友和住在这里的人献出我的生命。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110609400" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/jeff-monson-us-elite-mutes-russian-media-to-keep-ukraine-conflict-raging-on-1110609400.html?share-block=1110610233" data-title="&amp;quot;I talked to a man, a soldier, and I said, &amp;#x27;Why are you here?&amp;#x27; He picked up the ground and he kissed it and he said, &amp;#x27;This is Russia. This is ours, man. We&amp;#x27;ve got to protect this. My relatives live here, my grandparents, their grandparents. This is us. This is my love. I&amp;#x27;ll give my life for this place. I&amp;#x27;ll give my life for my country, for my fellow soldiers, for the people who live here.&amp;#x27;&amp;quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 26 May 2023 15:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/jeff-monson-us-elite-mutes-russian-media-to-keep-ukraine-conflict-raging-on-1110609400.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/jeff-monson-us-elite-mutes-russian-media-to-keep-ukraine-conflict-raging-on-1110609400.html<category>世界</category><category>杰夫蒙森</category><category>美国人</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>顿巴斯</category><category>综合格斗 (MMA)</category><category>北溪</category><category>人造卫星</category><category>美国领事馆</category><category>我们</category><category>观点</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Lavrov Confirms Commitment to Diplomatic Resolution of Ukraine Conflict]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110610910" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/10/1109575190_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_538078a139557738e36ec6b90624773d.jpg?source-sid=not_sputnik_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1109575141" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/lavrov-confirms-commitment-to-diplomatic-resolution-of-ukraine-conflict-1110610910.html?share-img=1109575141"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© 照片：俄罗斯外交部新闻处</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">俄罗斯外交部长谢尔盖·拉夫罗夫。档案照片</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt=" Russian Foreign Minister Sergey Lavrov. File photo  - Sputnik International, 1920, 26.05.2023" title="俄罗斯外长谢尔盖·拉夫罗夫。档案照片" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/10/1109575190_0:0:3072:1728_1920x0_80_0_0_3c6c900b35f288671fc5355b28e1b632.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/10/1109575190_0:0:3072:1728_640x0_80_0_0_7700118c4224c0ea3640248ad9a1ff2a.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/10/1109575190_0:0:3072:1728_1280x0_80_0_0_eae0c389e279c676da7e679cafb900f8.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/10/1109575190_0:0:3072:1728_1920x0_80_0_0_3c6c900b35f288671fc5355b28e1b632.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 照片：俄罗斯外交部新闻处</div>/ </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：俄罗斯外交部表示，俄罗斯外交部长谢尔盖·拉夫罗夫周五在会见中国政府欧亚事务特别代表李辉时，证实了莫斯科对通过外交途径解决乌克兰冲突的承诺。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “拉夫罗夫感谢中方<a href="https://sputniknews.in/20230421/chinas-ukraine-peace-plan-may-help-in-future-peace-efforts-moscow-1638263.html" target="_blank">在乌克兰危机上采取平衡立场</a>，高度赞赏北京愿意在解决问题上发挥积极作用。俄罗斯外长重申莫斯科致力于通过政治外交解决冲突，并指出严重的乌克兰方面及其西方策展人为恢复和谈设置了障碍，”该部表示。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 26 May 2023 14:38:01 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/lavrov-confirms-commitment-to-diplomatic-resolution-of-ukraine-conflict-1110610910.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/lavrov-confirms-commitment-to-diplomatic-resolution-of-ukraine-conflict-1110610910.html<category>俄罗斯在乌克兰的特别行动</category><category>乌克兰危机</category><category>外交</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[NATO to Upgrade Ukraine’s Partner Status Without Offering Membership – Reports]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110610315" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/07/07/1097069908_0:0:2395:1635_1440x900_80_0_1_740ea2df329b355dd9824f5d55571f00.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1097069891" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/nato-to-upgrade-ukraines-partner-status-without-offering-membership--reports-1110610315.html?share-img=1097069891"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / 乌克兰总统新闻办公室</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">乌克兰总统 Volodymyr Zelensky</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky  - Sputnik International, 1920, 26.05.2023" title="乌克兰总统泽连斯基" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/07/07/1097069908_0:117:2395:1464_1920x0_80_0_0_404c2bf28b0ef25f831626437dc6dc03.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/07/07/1097069908_0:117:2395:1464_640x0_80_0_0_862c04ecd6632409316f24d999722539.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/07/07/1097069908_0:117:2395:1464_1280x0_80_0_0_28989948db8edeb4d5d73d84013ee941.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/07/07/1097069908_0:117:2395:1464_1920x0_80_0_0_404c2bf28b0ef25f831626437dc6dc03.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © AP Photo / 乌克兰总统新闻办公室</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：据欧洲新闻媒体报道，北约计划在 7 月维尔纽斯峰会期间成立乌克兰-北约理事会来支持乌克兰，而不是向其提供成为正式成员的具体计划，基辅一再要求这样做周五，引用消息来源。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">北约外交官告诉媒体，该联盟必须在维持开放政策和支持基辅的愿望之间找到适当的平衡点，而不是直接承认该国加入该集团。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">拟议中的乌克兰-北约理事会应服务于此目的。消息人士称，基辅将成为该机构的“正式”成员，并将有更多机会与该联盟进行交流。报告称，乌克兰将能够进行更密切的情报共享、联合演习，并根据北约标准获得更多财政支持和发展本国武装部队的选择。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">北约外交官还认为，这种联合形式将使乌克兰在未来顺利过渡到成员国身份。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">此外，东欧北约成员国正在推动该集团向基辅提供一份清晰的路线图，以确保其在冲突后迅速接纳，而其他国家，可能包括最强大的国家，仍然不愿接受这一想法，认为这些决定报告称，2008 年布加勒斯特首脑会议<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/nato-not-ready-to-give-security-framework-to-ukraine-amid-ongoing-conflict-1110568482.html" target="_blank">声明乌克兰有朝一日将加入该联盟</a>，这已经足够了。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 5月初，乌克兰总统泽伦斯基<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230522/ukraine-a-long-way-from-being-allowed-to-join-nato---chancellor-scholz-1110525052.html" target="_blank">表示，乌克兰在冲突结束前不会加入北约</a>，但希望尽快收到西方盟友的邀请，加入北约。上个月，北约秘书长延斯·斯托尔滕贝格表示，由于所有北约成员国都支持乌克兰的雄心壮志，乌克兰最终将加入该集团。匈牙利总理欧尔班维克多拒绝了这个想法。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 2022年9月，泽连斯基宣布乌克兰将申请加速加入北约。克里姆林宫发言人德米特里·佩斯科夫表示，莫斯科正在密切关注事态发展，并回顾说，基辅对联盟的态度是<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230523/nato-gunning-to-destroy-russia-through-proxy-war-in-ukraine---medvedev-1110539806.html" target="_blank">俄罗斯去年在乌克兰开始军事行动的原因之一</a>。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 26 May 2023 13:50:14 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/nato-to-upgrade-ukraines-partner-status-without-offering-membership--reports-1110610315.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/nato-to-upgrade-ukraines-partner-status-without-offering-membership--reports-1110610315.html<category>军队</category><category>乌克兰危机</category><category>北约</category><category>俄罗斯-北约摊牌</category><category>美乌关系</category></item></channel></rss>